                                                                                                                                Table 4-1: Example Recovery Metrics


                                                                                                             Recovery Area                                           Example Metrics

                                                                                              Assessing Incident Damage and Cost              •        Costs due to the loss of competitive edge from the
                                                                                              Consider both direct and indirect costs;                 release of proprietary or sensitive information [dollar]
                                                                                              recovery damage and costs may be important      •        Legal costs [dollar]
                                                                                              evidence as part of a legal action.             •        Hardware, software, and labor costs to execute the
                                                                                                                                                       recovery plan [dollar]
                                                                                                                                              •        Costs relating to business disruption such as system
                                                                                                                                                       downtime; for example, lost employee productivity, lost
                                                                                                                                                       sales, etc. [time in hours, days, or weeks]
                                                                                                                                              •        Other consequential damages such as loss of brand
